+# ClientFactory Refactoring Status
+
+## Overview
+This document tracks the progress of replacing `SessionOption(s)` with `ClientFactoryBuilder`.
+
+## Completed Work
+
+### 1. Core Infrastructure ✅
+- **ClientFactoryBuilder** (`/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/ClientFactoryBuilder.java`)
+  - Fluent API for configuring ClientFactory
+  - Methods: `eventLoopGroup()`, `useDaemonThreads()`, `numWorkers()`, `connectTimeout()`, `idleTimeout()`, `sslContextCustomizer()`, `addressResolverGroupFactory()`, `connectionPoolListener()`, `useHttp2Preface()`, `useHttp1Pipelining()`
+  - `build()` method returns `DefaultClientFactory`
+
+### 2. New DefaultClientFactory ✅
+- **DefaultClientFactory** (`/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/DefaultClientFactory.java`)
+  - Replaces `AllInOneClientFactory`
+  - Package-local visibility
+  - Accepts builder configuration instead of `SessionOptions`
+  - Creates HTTP client factory internally
+  - Discovers and instantiates provider-based client factories (gRPC, Thrift)
+  - Implements all `ClientFactory` interface methods
+
+### 3. Updated HttpClientFactory ✅
+- **HttpClientFactory** (`/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/HttpClientFactory.java`)
+  - Merged functionality from `NonDecoratingClientFactory`
+  - Package-local visibility
+  - Accepts configuration parameters instead of `SessionOptions`
+  - Direct implementation of `ClientFactory` interface (no longer extends `AbstractClientFactory`)
+  - Added `validateScheme()` and `newEndpoint()` helper methods
+  - Added event loop management with daemon thread support
+
+### 4. Configuration Flags ✅
+- **Flags** (`/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/common/Flags.java`)
+  - Added `defaultNumServerBosses()` - default: 1
+  - Added `defaultNumServerWorkers()` - default: `Runtime.availableProcessors() * 2`
+  - Added `defaultNumClientWorkers()` - default: `Runtime.availableProcessors() * 2`
+  - Added `defaultConnectTimeoutMillis()` - default: 3200ms
+  - Added `defaultServerIdleTimeoutMillis()` - default: 10000ms
+  - Added `defaultClientIdleTimeoutMillis()` - default: 10000ms
+
+### 5. Renamed Class ✅
+- **KeyedChannelPoolHandlerWrapper** (`/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/pool/KeyedChannelPoolHandlerWrapper.java`)
+  - New class replacing `DecoratingKeyedChannelPoolHandler`
+  - **DecoratingKeyedChannelPoolHandler** now deprecated and extends `KeyedChannelPoolHandlerWrapper`
+
+### 6. Updated Provider Interface ✅
+- **ClientFactoryProvider** (`/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/ClientFactoryProvider.java`)
+  - Simplified signature: `newFactory(ClientFactory httpClientFactory)`
+  - Removed dependency on `SessionOptions` and dependency map
+  - Deprecated `dependencies()` method (no longer used)
+
+### 7. Updated Provider Implementations ✅
+- **HttpClientFactoryProvider** - deprecated (HTTP factory created directly by DefaultClientFactory)
+- **GrpcClientFactoryProvider** - updated to new signature
+- **THttpClientFactoryProvider** - updated to new signature
+
+### 8. Updated ClientFactory Interface ✅
+- **ClientFactory** (`/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/ClientFactory.java`)
+  - `DEFAULT` now uses `new ClientFactoryBuilder().build()`
+  - `closeDefault()` casts to `DefaultClientFactory` instead of `AllInOneClientFactory`
+  - Removed `options()` method
+  - Retained `eventLoopGroup()` and `eventLoopSupplier()`
+
+## Remaining Work
+
+### 1. Update Files Using SessionOptions ⚠️
+The following files still reference `SessionOptions` and need to be updated:
+
+- `/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/HttpClientDelegate.java`
+  - Line 175: `factory.options()` - needs to access factory configuration directly
+  - Line 180: `HttpSessionChannelFactory(bootstrap, options)` - needs configuration parameters
+  - Line 183: `options.poolHandlerDecorator()` - needs to get from factory
+
+- `/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/HttpClientPipelineConfigurator.java`
+  - Needs to access configuration from `HttpClientFactory` instead of `SessionOptions`
+
+- `/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/HttpSessionChannelFactory.java`
+  - Constructor accepts `SessionOptions` - needs to accept configuration parameters directly
+
+- `/testbed/core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/DecoratingClientFactory.java`
+  - May need updates if it references `SessionOptions`
+
+### 2. Deprecate/Remove Old Classes ⚠️
+- **NonDecoratingClientFactory** - should be deprecated (functionality merged into `HttpClientFactory`)
+- **AllInOneClientFactory** - should be deprecated (replaced by `DefaultClientFactory`)
+- **SessionOption** - should be deprecated/removed
+- **SessionOptions** - should be deprecated/removed
+- **SessionOptionValue** - should be deprecated/removed
+
+### 3. Update Tests ⚠️
+- All test files that construct `ClientFactory` with `SessionOptions`
+- Tests in core module
+- Tests in grpc module
+- Tests in thrift module
+- Examples and documentation
+
+### 4. Update Documentation ⚠️
+- Javadoc references to `SessionOption(s)`
+- Migration guide for users
+- Code examples
+
+## Migration Guide for Users
+
+### Before:
+```java
+SessionOptions options = SessionOptions.of(
+    SessionOption.CONNECT_TIMEOUT.newValue(Duration.ofSeconds(5)),
+    SessionOption.IDLE_TIMEOUT.newValue(Duration.ofSeconds(30)),
+    SessionOption.USE_HTTP2_PREFACE.newValue(true)
+);
+ClientFactory factory = new AllInOneClientFactory(options);
+```
+
+### After:
+```java
+ClientFactory factory = new ClientFactoryBuilder()
+    .connectTimeout(Duration.ofSeconds(5))
+    .idleTimeout(Duration.ofSeconds(30))
+    .useHttp2Preface(true)
+    .build();
+```
+
+## Implementation Notes
+
+1. **Package-local factories**: `HttpClientFactory` and `DefaultClientFactory` are now package-local to prevent direct instantiation. Users should use `ClientFactoryBuilder`.
+
+2. **Provider simplification**: Providers now receive a single `HttpClientFactory` parameter instead of `SessionOptions` and a dependency map.
+
+3. **Internal configuration access**: `HttpClientFactory` and `DefaultClientFactory` expose package-local accessor methods (e.g., `connectTimeout()`, `idleTimeout()`) for internal use by classes like `HttpClientDelegate`.
+
+4. **Backwards compatibility**: Old classes are deprecated but not removed to maintain source compatibility during migration.
+
+## Files Modified
+
+### Core module:
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.common.Flags`
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.ClientFactory`
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.ClientFactoryBuilder` (new)
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.ClientFactoryProvider`
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.DefaultClientFactory` (new)
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.HttpClientFactory`
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.HttpClientFactoryProvider`
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.pool.KeyedChannelPoolHandlerWrapper` (new)
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.pool.DecoratingKeyedChannelPoolHandler` (deprecated)
+
+### gRPC module:
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.grpc.GrpcClientFactoryProvider`
+
+### Thrift module:
+- `com.linecorp.armeria.client.thrift.THttpClientFactoryProvider`
+
+## Next Steps
+
+1. Update `HttpClientDelegate` to access configuration from `HttpClientFactory` directly
+2. Update `HttpSessionChannelFactory` constructor signature
+3. Update `HttpClientPipelineConfigurator`
+4. Deprecate old factory classes
+5. Mark SessionOption classes as deprecated
+6. Fix all compilation errors
+7. Update and run tests
+8. Update documentation
